首先你先找到一批的不同学习风格的学习者

84
00:03:40,620 --> 00:03:43,800
with at least two different learning styles, say visual and auditory
假设他们的学习风格有视觉和听觉的

85
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:48,840
and then randomly assign learners to one of two educational presentations,
然后把他们随机分到两个课堂里

86
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:50,870
one visual, one auditory.
一个视觉教学，一个听觉教学

87
00:03:50,870 --> 00:03:54,700
So for half of the students, the experience will match their learning style
那这样一半的学生会以他们的学习方式学习

88
00:03:54,700 --> 00:03:57,000
and for the other half it won't.
另外一半则不会

89
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:59,930
And then you give everyone the same test.
在此之后给他们一份测试题

90
00:03:59,930 --> 00:04:02,350
If the learning style hypothesis is correct,
如果学习风格的假说是对的

91
00:04:02,350 --> 00:04:05,000
